        <h3 id="overview">Health Status Information Mapping -&gt; FHIR Profiles (CZ PS)</h3>

        <p>
            Below is a browsable diagram showing how the Health Status Information model is realized by the HL7 FHIR profiles defined in this guide. The mapping covers immunization history, past health problems, and general anamnesis.
        </p>

